</head>

<body>
  <!-- 네비바, 스크롤탑, 스크롤바 ejs 호출 -->
  <%- include("navbar.ejs") %>

  <!-- S:상단 배너 -->
  <br>
  <div class="container-fluid" style="padding: 0px;">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
        <img src="/static/img/userpage_banner_top.png" style="width: 100%">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- E:상단 배너 -->

  <!-- S:정렬, 필터 -->
  <div class="container-fluid my-3 beer-search">
    <form class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger mr-3" style="float: right;" id="btnSort">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor"
            class="bi bi-sort-alpha-down" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M10.082 5.629 9.664 7H8.598l1.789-5.332h1.234L13.402 7h-1.12l-.419-1.371h-1.781zm1.57-.785L11 2.687h-.047l-.652 2.157h1.351z" />
            <path
              d="M12.96 14H9.028v-.691l2.579-3.72v-.054H9.098v-.867h3.785v.691l-2.567 3.72v.054h2.645V14zM4.5 2.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v9.793l-1.146-1.147a.5.5 0 0 0-.708.708l2 1.999.007.007a.497.497 0 0 0 .7-.006l2-2a.5.5 0 0 0-.707-.708L4.5 12.293V2.5z" />
          </svg> sort
        </button>
      </div>
      <input class="col form-control mr-sm-2" type="search" placeholder="Just type a name" aria-label="Search"
        id="search">
      <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-success my-0 my-sm-0" type="submit">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor"
            class="bi bi-x-square mb-1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path
              d="M14 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h12zM2 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2z" />
            <path
              d="M4.646 4.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0L8 7.293l2.646-2.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708L8.707 8l2.647 2.646a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708L8 8.707l-2.646 2.647a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L7.293 8 4.646 5.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z" />
          </svg> RESET
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <!-- E:정렬, 필터 -->

  <!-- S:코멘트 나열 -->
  <div class="container-fluid" style="padding: 0px;">
    <div class="card-deck row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4 justify-content-center">
      <div class="card-frame col-sm-10 col-md-5">
        <div class="card card-shadow h-100 mb-3">
          <div class="row g-0 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-4">
              <img src="/static/img/beerimg/heineken.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start">
            </div>
            <div class="vr my-3 text-muted"></div>
            <div class="col-7">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="col card-name"><a>Heineken</a></div>
                <h5 class="card-rating">★★★★☆</h5>
                <p class="card-comment">
                  적당한 씁쓸한 맛과 조금 단 맛 때문인지 물리지 않고 끝까지 맛을 보며 마시기 좋다. 언제나 실패 없는 안전빵(?)
                </p>
                <p class="card-date">
                  <small class="text-muted">2022-08-13</small>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-frame col-sm-10 col-md-5">
        <div class="card card-shadow h-100 mb-3">
          <div class="row g-0 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-4">
              <img src="/static/img/beerimg/hoegaarden rosee.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="vr my-3 text-muted"></div>
            <div class="col-7">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-name"><a>Hoegaarden Rosee</a></div>
                <h5 class="card-rating">★★★★★</h5>
                <p class="card-comment">
                  라즈베리 향이 약간 첨가됨. 신기한 마음에 도전해 봄. 기대감이 크지 않아서 그런지 만족. 오히려 자주 먹기에는 ㅎㅎ
                </p>
                <p class="card-date">
                  <small class="text-muted">2022-08-02</small>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-frame col-sm-10 col-md-5">
        <div class="card card-shadow h-100 mb-3">
          <div class="row g-0 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-4">
              <img src="/static/img/beerimg/asahi.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="vr my-3 text-muted"></div>
            <div class="col-7">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="col card-name"><a>Asahi</a></div>
                <h5 class="card-rating">★★☆☆☆</h5>
                <p class="card-comment">
                  기대감이 큰 상태로 맛봐서 그런지 실망이 컸던 기억이 남음. 조합을 바꿔서 언젠가 다시 도전해볼까.
                </p>
                <p class="card-date">
                  <small class="text-muted">2022-07-18</small>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-frame col-sm-10 col-md-5">
        <div class="card card-shadow h-100 mb-3">
          <div class="row g-0 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-4">
              <img src="/static/img/beerimg/edelweiss.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="vr my-3 text-muted"></div>
            <div class="col-7">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="col card-name"><a>Edelweiss</a></div>
                <h5 class="card-rating">★★★★☆</h5>
                <p class="card-comment">
                  "..."
                </p>
                <p class="card-date">
                  <small class="text-muted">2022-07-04</small>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-frame col-sm-10 col-md-5">
        <div class="card card-shadow h-100 mb-3">
          <div class="row g-0 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-4">
              <img src="/static/img/beerimg/carlsberg.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="vr my-3 text-muted"></div>
            <div class="col-7">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="col card-name"><a>Carlsberg</a></div>
                <h5 class="card-rating">★★★★☆</h5>
                <p class="card-comment">
                  쓴 맛 싫어하는 사람들이 많이 마신다고 들었음. 가볍게 마시기에 좋았다.
                </p>
                <p class="card-date">
                  <small class="text-muted">2022-07-01</small>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- E:코멘트 나열 -->

  <br>
  <br>
  <%- include("footer.ejs") %>

  <script>
    // this overrides `contains` to make it case insensitive
    jQuery.expr[':'].contains = function (a, i, m) {
      return jQuery(a).text().toUpperCase()
        .indexOf(m[3].toUpperCase()) >= 0;
    };

    $('#search').keyup(function () {
      $('.card').parent().removeClass('d-none');
      var filter = $(this).val(); // get the value of the input, which we filter on
      $('.card-deck').find('.card .card-name:not(:contains("' + filter + '"))').parent().parent().parent().parent().parent().addClass('d-none');
    })

    $('#btnSort').click(function () {
      $('.card-deck .card-frame').sort(function (a, b) {
        return $(a).find(".card-name").text() > $(b).find(".card-name").text() ? 1 : -1;
      }).appendTo(".card-deck");
    })
  </script>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>